search_results.title: About
search_results.snippet: Justin Taylor is the author of the novel Reboot, the memoir Riding with the Ghost, the novel The Gospel of Anarchy, and two collections of short fiction.

search_results.title: Justin Torres
search_results.snippet: Justin Torres is the author of Blackouts, which won the 2023 National Book Award for Fiction, was a finalist for the LA Times Book Prize.

search_results.title: Justin Wren
search_results.snippet: A speaker to inspire your audience like never before, that's Justin Wren. While doing so, he teaches personal techniques to confront any adversity.
